{"start": 0.0, "end": 8.0, "text": "I hope you've had the opportunity to review our shareholder deck to get a sense of what an incredible year 2020 3 was for Spotify.", "sentiment": "POSITIVE", "score": 0.99775367975235, "signed_score": 0.99775367975235, "positive_prob": 0.99775367975235, "negative_prob": 0.0022463202476500355}
{"start": 8.0, "end": 13.0, "text": "Throughout the year, we noticed some really significant milestones and set numerous records.", "sentiment": "POSITIVE", "score": 0.9998273849487304, "signed_score": 0.9998273849487304, "positive_prob": 0.9998273849487304, "negative_prob": 0.00017261505126964227}
{"start": 13.0, "end": 20.0, "text": "This included 113 million net ads on the MU side and premium net ads of 3...", "sentiment": "NEGATIVE", "score": 0.9851952791213988, "signed_score": -0.9851952791213988, "positive_prob": 0.014804720878601185, "negative_prob": 0.9851952791213988}
{"start": 20.0, "end": 36.0, "text": "And there's no question that we had to make some difficult decisions that put us on track to achieve our goal of being a consistently profitable company, but by taking these steps, I'm super confident in where we're heading.", "sentiment": "POSITIVE", "score": 0.9996665716171264, "signed_score": 0.9996665716171264, "positive_prob": 0.9996665716171264, "negative_prob": 0.0003334283828736462}
{"start": 36.0, "end": 40.0, "text": "So looking to 2024, you should expect a consumer.", "sentiment": "NEGATIVE", "score": 0.9910927414894104, "signed_score": -0.9910927414894104, "positive_prob": 0.0089072585105896, "negative_prob": 0.9910927414894104}
{"start": 40.0, "end": 53.0, "text": "In addition to what you saw in 2023, strong product development, which leads to strong growth, but with an increased focus on monetization and efficiency, which in turn drives profitability.", "sentiment": "POSITIVE", "score": 0.999237060546875, "signed_score": 0.999237060546875, "positive_prob": 0.999237060546875, "negative_prob": 0.000762939453125}
{"start": 53.0, "end": 58.0, "text": "And I know some of you may start to wonder if we're sacrificing growth for profitability.", "sentiment": "NEGATIVE", "score": 0.997292935848236, "signed_score": -0.997292935848236, "positive_prob": 0.002707064151764027, "negative_prob": 0.997292935848236}
{"start": 58.0, "end": 66.0, "text": "In some terms, we believe that the real value of Spotify is in solving problems at the intersection between creators and consumers.", "sentiment": "POSITIVE", "score": 0.5669909119606018, "signed_score": 0.5669909119606018, "positive_prob": 0.5669909119606018, "negative_prob": 0.4330090880393982}
{"start": 66.0, "end": 70.0, "text": "With scale, there will be even more opportunities to do so.", "sentiment": "POSITIVE", "score": 0.9948549270629884, "signed_score": 0.9948549270629884, "positive_prob": 0.9948549270629884, "negative_prob": 0.005145072937011608}
{"start": 70.0, "end": 74.0, "text": "Therefore, growth is still the most important thing we can deliver.", "sentiment": "POSITIVE", "score": 0.9998427629470824, "signed_score": 0.9998427629470824, "positive_prob": 0.9998427629470824, "negative_prob": 0.0001572370529175915}
{"start": 74.0, "end": 79.0, "text": "In Q4, we became the number two provider of audiobooks behind.", "sentiment": "POSITIVE", "score": 0.9146573543548584, "signed_score": 0.9146573543548584, "positive_prob": 0.9146573543548584, "negative_prob": 0.0853426456451416}
{"start": 79.0, "end": 82.0, "text": "Which is notable given how entrenched the legacy players are.", "sentiment": "POSITIVE", "score": 0.9996446371078492, "signed_score": 0.9996446371078492, "positive_prob": 0.9996446371078492, "negative_prob": 0.0003553628921507679}
{"start": 82.0, "end": 84.0, "text": "Q4 is a very strong quarter.", "sentiment": "POSITIVE", "score": 0.999710977077484, "signed_score": 0.999710977077484, "positive_prob": 0.999710977077484, "negative_prob": 0.00028902292251598016}
{"start": 84.0, "end": 87.0, "text": "And maybe you grew like 28 million to 602 million.", "sentiment": "NEGATIVE", "score": 0.6263163089752197, "signed_score": -0.6263163089752197, "positive_prob": 0.3736836910247803, "negative_prob": 0.6263163089752197}
{"start": 87.0, "end": 91.0, "text": "And we had a 10 million net subscribers finishing up 236 million.", "sentiment": "POSITIVE", "score": 0.9825875163078308, "signed_score": 0.9825875163078308, "positive_prob": 0.9825875163078308, "negative_prob": 0.01741248369216919}
{"start": 91.0, "end": 96.0, "text": "With the MU and subscriber growth continued to be above our historical trend and outperform forecast.", "sentiment": "POSITIVE", "score": 0.9681490659713744, "signed_score": 0.9681490659713744, "positive_prob": 0.9681490659713744, "negative_prob": 0.0318509340286256}
{"start": 96.0, "end": 98.0, "text": "Looking ahead to the first quarter.", "sentiment": "POSITIVE", "score": 0.9995989203453064, "signed_score": 0.9995989203453064, "positive_prob": 0.9995989203453064, "negative_prob": 0.0004010796546936035}
{"start": 98.0, "end": 108.0, "text": "For guidance, we are forecasting 618 million MU, an increase of 16 million from Q4, and 230 million subscribers, an increase of 3 million over Q4.", "sentiment": "POSITIVE", "score": 0.8479767441749573, "signed_score": 0.8479767441749573, "positive_prob": 0.8479767441749573, "negative_prob": 0.15202325582504272}
