{"start": 150.0, "end": 158.0, "text": "So I think the general story just to be candid here with all of you on the line is that what we've seen is that while exclusivities were.", "sentiment": "POSITIVE", "score": 0.6599607467651367, "signed_score": 0.6599607467651367, "positive_prob": 0.6599607467651367, "negative_prob": 0.3400392532348633}
