{"start": 210.0, "end": 218.0, "text": "So internally and externally, I think the biggest surprise has been the type of titles that resonate with consumers.", "sentiment": "POSITIVE", "score": 0.998817265033722, "signed_score": 0.998817265033722, "positive_prob": 0.998817265033722, "negative_prob": 0.0011827349662779651}
